{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What's that sound coming from the basement....?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GLITCH DADDY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> is the new <strong>fever dream</strong> of a game by <strong>Sad Mask Party</strong>, the <i>twisted</i> brains behind <strong>Mango</strong> and <strong>The Lotus Holidays</strong>. It is a surreal, elusive, <i>highly</i> immersive and <i>just slightly</i> distorted tale of mystery, friendship, romance, solitude, trying and failing, overcoming obstacles, and all around, <strong>love</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676440/extras/glitchred.gif?t=1733247411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is presented as a first person adventure, featuring <strong>atmospheric exploration</strong>, puzzles, some <strong>fun action sequences and fights</strong>, interactive dialogue, deconstructed psychology, <strong>dreamy psychedelia</strong>, a <strong>big variety of off-beat characters</strong>, terminally weird vibes and <strong>an equal mixture of horror(ish) and humorous elements</strong>. The graphics are PS1-inspired, but with a healthy dose of surrealism and liminality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story starts through a dream where you meet <strong>Glitch Daddy</strong>, a strange creature informing you about <strong>the world's end coming really, really soon</strong>. You go on to wake up, and embark on a wild journey where the truth will be revealed, through a series of <strong>weird</strong>, unexpected twists and turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676440/extras/glitchcity.gif?t=1733247411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drenched in a <strong>thick vibe of nostalgia</strong>, <strong>Glitch Daddy</strong> seamlessly jumps from the memories of an idealized childhood, to a complicated adulthood, and the cosmic, deconstructed<strong> dreamscapes</strong> of a timeless oblivion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Also, you get to kill monsters and pet doggos. ;)</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"BLOB","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/926e7814f63f5d0489553c244f4b7e7d8cb12c80.jpg"},{"name":"WAKE UP (?)","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/f273fbcd09b40a884306c2f742d0a1f235ab2855.jpg"},{"name":"MESSAGE IN A BOTTLE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/09e4e46305b0191ca166cd4ff6f136602bab2351.jpg"},{"name":"EVIL GENIUS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/5b3311f90b66e0d16cec3061395501ddad701601.jpg"},{"name":"ROADKILL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/f00ddeb561ef799443faa55f0061d1dd0153637b.jpg"},{"name":"TRASH COMPLETIONIST","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/ce12352cc74414f0e5a33450d33ecb7ba2ffa81d.jpg"},{"name":"SECURITY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/f1d5efa647f915879e31798739eaa9b65a971a99.jpg"},{"name":"BLOB:REVISITED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/addd425dc9d809a585a9fa2502d3e2a6abfe6183.jpg"},{"name":"CAVE DADDY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/a02b631c3e5090284905c87991e5dc0c54a14764.jpg"},{"name":"DEBUG","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2676440/76ef58a349d9b0c249a4346b184863fa06851f04.jpg"}],"total":18},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676440/page_bg_